description: April's fools/joke-themed community map pack featuring twelve not-to-be-taken-seriously levels with deliberately goofy or trollish settings or gameplay. It is based on the progs_dump mod (included) and comes with three demos, many custom sounds, music, and skyboxes. The map sources are included as well.
notes: Some of these maps require a source port with increased limits.
